ddress this issue.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Rust:<\/strong>Rust is often overlooked and will only be noticed when something doesn\u2019t work anymore. If you notice signs pointing to an oxidation problem, call our company.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Damaged Mortar Joints:<\/strong> When mortar deteriorates, chimney masonry becomes exposed to moisture. Call MT Chimney Repair Chicago professionals to have it fixed.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rowItem col-md-6 col-sm-12 cellLeft animate animate-fadein animate-moveright inherit btTextIndent\"  ><div class=\"rowItemContent\" ><div class = \"btImage\"><img src=\"https:\/\/mtmasonrychicago.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/chimney-repair-scaled.jpg\" class=\"btImage image-13\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><section id=\"bt_section627ea7d8b26de\"  class=\"boldSection topSpaced bottomSmallSpaced gutter\" ><div class=\"port\"><div class=\"boldCell\"><div class=\"boldRow \" ><div class=\"rowItem col-sm-12 col-md-12 cellCenter animate animate-fadein inherit\"  ><div class=\"rowItemContent\" ><div class=\"btText\"><header class=\"header medium\">\n<h2><span class=\"dash\"><span class=\"h2content\" style=\"font-size: 30px; font-weight: 300;\">The importance of Chimney Repair Chicago, IL<\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/header>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><section id=\"about\"  class=\"boldSection divider bottomSpaced gutter block-about border-bottom50\" ><div class=\"port\"><div class=\"boldCell\"><div class=\"boldRow \" ><div class=\"rowItem col-md-6 col-sm-12 cellLeft animate animate-fadein animate-moveright inherit btTextIndent\"  ><div class=\"rowItemContent\" ><div class = \"btImage\"><img src=\"https:\/\/mtmasonrychicago.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/Chimneys-12-scaled.j